high_descs: Turn around and face the table behind.
Grab the spatula off of the table.
Turn right and walk to the stove.
Place the spatula in the pot in front.
Grab the pot off of the stove.
Turn right then walk and face the table on the left.
Place the pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the pot with the spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the spatula on the left side of the table.
Turn right and go straight, to go to the stove.
Put the spatula in the pot on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the spatula in it.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left to approach the table.
Put the pot on the table, to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to table.
Pick up spatula, located on the left side of the table, to the left of the potato and below the knife.
Turn right, walk to stove.
Place spatula in pot on lower right burner on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the spatula in it.
Turn right, go to sink.  Turn left, go to table.
Put pot with spatula in it on the table to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put spatula in pot, move both to a table.
